{"word":"ἁρμόδιος","slug":"ἁρμόδιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἁρμόδιος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἁρμόζω'><el>ἁρμόζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>fitting together</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>well-fitting, accordant, agreeable</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ως</el>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}